By the way, it's a good idea to always check for traps before trying to open a door. Do this with the command ('use_skill find traps), which is often bound to the 'f' key.  If you find a trap, you can try to disarm it with ('use_skill disarm traps). You can only find and disable traps if you have those skills.

Some doors will open when you walk up to them, then close after a moment. Be careful not to get crushed by standing in the doorway too long!
