=== Inventory ===

Stop and take a look at your inventory for a moment.  If you started the game with any armor or a hand-to-hand weapon like a sword, you probably should ready them now. (In most clients you do this by double-clicking.) Don't make the mistake of many new players, and run into your first monsters naked and empty-handed. :-)
endmsg
